title: BIP 66 (b). DIGG TCL Budgeting
body:
How much DIGG and BTC should Badger contribute to establishing treasury controlled liquidity for DIGG?

1) 20% DIGG Supply Plus Corresponding BTC 
~ 78.4 DIGG + 67.1 BTC; 4.9 $M worth of liquidity
2) 15% DIGG Supply Plus Corresponding BTC 
~ 58.8 DIGG + 50.3 BTC; 3.7 $M worth of liquidity
3) 10% DIGG Supply Plus Corresponding BTC 
~ 39.2 DIGG + 32.6 BTC; 2.5 $M worth of liquidity
4) 5% DIGG Supply Plus Corresponding BTC 
~ 19.6 DIGG + 16.78 BTC; 1.2 $M worth of liquidity
5) none

The method to decide the outcome is Ranked Choice Voting.
Link to the Discussions: https://forum.badger.finance/t/bip-66-revise-digg-emissions-fund-kpi-options-and-establish-tcl/4860
